      "updated": 1777281771727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now we have 3 functions that can tell this but they require a specific structure\nso we need to somehow fetch that strucure, that we can do with LLM, we know LLM can\nonly predict result, they can't run the code so we will tell our LLM just covert this\nline in structure format so that we can call funtion accordingly, we will tell LLM we have\n4 function of names bla bla .. for these you just need to tell which function I need to trigger. this concept is \nwhat we call is AI agent.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now we have 3 functions that can tell this but they require a specific structure\nso we need to somehow fetch that strucure, that we can do with LLM, we know LLM can\nonly predict result, they can't run the code so we will tell our LLM just covert this\nline in structure format so that we can call funtion accordingly, we will tell LLM we have\n4 function of names bla bla .. for these you just need to tell which function I need to trigger. this concept is \nwhat we call is AI agent.",
