      "text": "AI agent basically means it has access of funtions and LLM. this LLM can't call directly\nthese function, LLM can't call any tool by itself, SO AI agent is nothing but LLM with\nexternal tools or functions.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AI agent basically means it has access of funtions and LLM. this LLM can't call directly\nthese function, LLM can't call any tool by itself, SO AI agent is nothing but LLM with\nexternal tools or functions.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
