      "versionNonce": 1349589430,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777282346751,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How we will get to know LLM is asking to call external tool or function or it is a final output?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How we will get to know LLM is asking to call external tool or function or it is a final output?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vU1hoKw-7tc4sKLNKCxad",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1424.9029962242125,
      "y": 71055.21302986321,
      "width": 1078,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bqF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 668786538,
      "version": 321,
      "versionNonce": 1903376362,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777282801830,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we can check documentation of google ai studio they mentioned if in response there is functionCall\nthen it is asking to call function otherwise it is not.\n\nif response.functionCall:\n    call function\nelse\n    print output\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we can check documentation of google ai studio they mentioned if in response there is functionCall\nthen it is asking to call function otherwise it is not.\n\nif response.functionCall:\n    call function\nelse\n    print output\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xsyoLyY7z7EPA_8bWNPbm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1323.9517882285197,
      "y": 71311.58290112838,
      "width": 913,
      "height": 2025,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bqG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 408694006,
      "version": 1038,
      "versionNonce": 1811352374,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "QIHx3GjNzYJNhTsEyDJrI",
          "type": "arrow"
        },
        {
          "id": "GvIAIeq4Pm7ClGmg8OPz0",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1777284064014,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "sum_declaration = {\n    \"name\": \"sum\", -> function name\n    \"description\": \"Get sum of two numbers\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"num1\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be first number for addition ex 10\",\n            },\n            \"num2\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be second number for addition ex 20\",\n            },\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"num1\", \"num2\"],\n    },\n} \n\n\n\nprime_declaration = {\n    \"name\": \"is_prime\",\n    \"description\": \"Get if number is prime or not\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"num\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be the number to find prime or not ex: 13\",\n            }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"num\"],\n    },\n} \n\n\n\ncrypto_declaration = {\n    \"name\": \"get_crypto_price\",\n    \"description\": \"Get the current price of any crypto currency like bitcoin\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"coin\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be the crypto currency name like bitcoin \",\n            }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"coin\"],\n    },\n} \n\n\n\n\nfrom google import genai\nfrom google.genai import types\n\n\n\nclient = genai.Client(api_key=\"AIzaSyCiaVzwz9Kg_LHDl9JuhRE5MKOFtMDlnis\")\n\nresponse = client.models.generate_content(\n    model=\"gemini-2.5-flash-lite\", \n    contents= history_of_chat,\n    config : types.GenerateContentConfig(\n            tools=[sum_declaration, prime_declaration, crypto_declaration]\n            )\n    \n)\n\n\n\n\nif response.functionCall and len(response.functionCall) > 0:\n    name, args = response.functionCall[0]\n    functionCall = name\n    result = functionCall(args)\nelse:\n    print(response.text)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "sum_declaration = {\n    \"name\": \"sum\", -> function name\n    \"description\": \"Get sum of two numbers\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"num1\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be first number for addition ex 10\",\n            },\n            \"num2\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be second number for addition ex 20\",\n            },\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"num1\", \"num2\"],\n    },\n} \n\n\n\nprime_declaration = {\n    \"name\": \"is_prime\",\n    \"description\": \"Get if number is prime or not\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"num\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be the number to find prime or not ex: 13\",\n            }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"num\"],\n    },\n} \n\n\n\ncrypto_declaration = {\n    \"name\": \"get_crypto_price\",\n    \"description\": \"Get the current price of any crypto currency like bitcoin\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"coin\": {\n                \"type\": \"Number\",\n                \"description\": \"It will be the crypto currency name like bitcoin \",\n            }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"coin\"],\n    },\n} \n\n\n\n\nfrom google import genai\nfrom google.genai import types\n\n\n\nclient = genai.Client(api_key=\"AIzaSyCiaVzwz9Kg_LHDl9JuhRE5MKOFtMDlnis\")\n\nresponse = client.models.generate_content(\n    model=\"gemini-2.5-flash-lite\", \n    contents= history_of_chat,\n    config : types.GenerateContentConfig(\n            tools=[sum_declaration, prime_declaration, crypto_declaration]\n            )\n    \n)\n\n\n\n\nif response.functionCall and len(response.functionCall) > 0:\n    name, args = response.functionCall[0]\n    functionCall = name\n    result = functionCall(args)\nelse:\n    print(response.text)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
